OL,3,CScottish rugby legend Scott Hastings
OL,4,Cdies aged 61
OL,6,FScottish rugby union legend Scott
OL,7,FHastings has died at the age of 61.
OL,9,FA statement released by his son Corey
OL,10,Fand daughter Kerry-Anne said he died
OL,11,Fon Sunday following complications
OL,12,Farising from cancer treatment.
OL,14,FHastings revealed he had been
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with non-Hodgkin's lymphoma
OL,16,Fin 2022.
OL,18,F"We are saddened to inform you that
OL,19,FScott passed away peacefully
OL,20,Fsurrounded by family on the morning of
OL,21,FSunday, May 17," the statement read.
OL,26,@}D@PO]
