OL,3,CScottish rugby legend Scott Hastings
OL,4,Cdies aged 61
OL,6,F"This also marked his late wife
OL,7,FJenny's birthday which speaks louder
OL,8,Fthan words that he is safe and with
OL,9,Fhis beloved Jenny.
OL,11,F"Scott was undergoing cancer treatment
OL,12,Fand due to complications deteriorated
OL,13,Fextremely quickly. Despite every
OL,14,Feffort by the incredible team at the
OL,15,FWestern General ICU, he passed away
OL,16,Fpeacefully and pain free.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
