OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779087942
OL,3,CScottish rugby legend Scott Hastings
OL,4,Cdies aged 61
OL,6,F"At this time, the family ask everyone
OL,7,Fto give them space to process and
OL,8,Fmanage their energies and ask for
OL,9,Ftheir privacy to be respected. More
OL,10,Finformation will be shared in due
OL,11,Fcourse to celebrate Scott's incredible
OL,12,Flife."
OL,14,FHastings won 65 caps in an 11-year
OL,15,Finternational career that began in
OL,16,F1986, and he was part of the most
OL,17,Frecent Scotland team to win the Grand
OL,18,FSlam in 1990.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@FO]
