OL,3,CScottish rugby legend Scott Hastings
OL,4,Cdies aged 61
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHe toured twice with the British and
OL,12,FIrish Lions in 1989 and 1993, and
OL,13,Fplayed alongside his older brother
OL,14,FGavin in the Five Nations.
OL,16,FHastings made his international debut
OL,17,Fagainst France and hung up his boots
OL,18,Fafter facing England in 1997, before
OL,19,Fgoing on to become a respected
OL,20,Fbroadcaster.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
