OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779087942
OL,3,CScottish rugby legend Scott Hastings
OL,4,Cdies aged 61
OL,6,F"My association with Scott and his
OL,7,Fbrother Gavin was always special for
OL,8,Fme," former Scotland and Lions head
OL,9,Fcoach Sir Ian McGeechan said.
OL,11,F"We came into the Scotland set-up,
OL,12,Fmyself as coach, and Scott and Gavin
OL,13,Fas players, at the same time. We came
OL,14,Fin together and we grew together.
OL,16,F"I remember Scott on the Lions tours
OL,17,Ftaking an absolute lead. He was so
OL,18,Fsingle-minded and determined about
OL,19,Fwinning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@DO]sD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
