PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779087942
OL,3,CScottish rugby legend Scott Hastings
OL,4,Cdies aged 61
OL,6,F"He was very much your right-hand man,
OL,7,Fgiven what he did on the field. I
OL,8,Fstill remember the Grand Slam game
OL,9,Fagainst England in 1990.
OL,11,F"There was his Lions team-mate from
OL,12,Fthe previous year, Jerry Guscott, in
OL,13,Fthe England team, but Scott gave
OL,14,Fnothing away to him whatsoever.
OL,16,F"Whatever jersey Scott wore, he just
OL,17,Fmade it better."
